The mission of Jesheua, John, Miriam and the Maji was intended to prepare the Angelic Humans of Earth to fulfill the Christos Realignment Mission during the anticipated 2000-2017 SAC. In 23 AD Jesheua and his Maji were attacked by the Annu- Melchizedek Hyksos and Hassa Leviathan King races, in an event called the Essene Divide, which rendered them unable to fully complete their intended journey to the lands previously known as northern Lohas At- lantis, the location of Earth’s Star Gate-11. • To protect the Arc of the Covenant Gold Box and star gate tools, John and Miriam completed part of the journey to Lohas, burying the Arc of the Covenant Gold Box and tools in the area now known as the Vale of Pew- 314
